name: import
title: Import a Plandefinition
description:
Import a Plandefinition
### Parameters
- planDefinitionPackage: Binary package produced by the export operation
### Output
Bundle containing the created and existing resources:
- PlanDefinitions (without: co-author, missing target audiences and missing intended organizations, with: owner set to current Organization, and status DRAFT) 
- ActivityDefinitions (without: co-author, missing target audiences and missing intended organizations, with: owner set to current organization, and status set to DRAFT) 
- Questionnaires (without: co-author, missing target audiences, missing intended organizations, with: owner set to current organization, publisher set to current user name, and status set to DRAFT).
If the main plan already exists on the target system, the import is aborted.
If triage rules are missing on the target system, the import fails.

Imports QFFD DocumentReference into Document-Transformation service. Libraries and Organizations are used to find the corresponding resources on the target system.
